Why Choose Cars24 Owned Cars in Australia for Your Used Car Purchase


100% Online

Getting a Used car with Cars24 is a convenient and easy option because everything is online. You can browse, compare and purchase from our wide range of used cars without stepping out. We also have a Used car Trade in value option.

Free Warranty

Cars24 certified pre-owned cars purchased through Cars24 come with a complimentary three-month warranty. 

Vehicle Inspection

At CARS24, Cars24 certified second-hand car undergoes a 300+ point inspection to ensure reliability and quality. You can buy used cars from CARS24 with trust and confidence, knowing each vehicle is thoroughly verified before being listed.

Test Drive 

If you want to get behind the wheel before final yes to your Cars24 certified pre-owned car, you can book a test drive at a Cars24 hub and experience your car before sale.

7 Day Return Policy

Due to any reason you changed your mind, you can simply return your Cars24 certified second hand car within 7 days for a full refund. No questions asked.

Transparency

We believe in honest pricing. All the used cars listed on the website for sale include full details like specifications, reports and costs. Our pricing shows a clear breakout, so that you know what you are paying for, like taxes, etc.

Ownership Transfer Support

No more paperwork issues because Cars24 manages the registration, finance settlement and transfer for your Cars24 certified second hand car, so that you can enjoy your new ride.

Extended Warranty

Want more protection for your car? Extend your coverage with Cars24's additional services. We cover all variants and model, whether it’s Toyota Hybrid car or Mazda car. 

 

Buying a Cars24 Certified Used Car Online in Australia- Step by Step

  1. Browse our wide inventory

    Explore a wide range of selection of Toyota, BMW, Audi, Mercedes-Benz, Honda, Hyundai and many more. Each car we offer comes with extensive inspection and PPSR reports for well-informed decision. 

  2. Start the process online or book a test drive

    Our process is 100% online but if you test the car you wish to drive, you can book a test drive with us. You will have to book a slot and fill in relevant information for test drive and if you don’t want to test, you can simply choose to make purchase online.

  3. Get finance (if needed)

    If you require a loan, Cars24 offers pre-approved loans as well. Our process is quick and can be easily done alongside car selection.

  4. Make payment and complete purchase

    Finalise your purchase by selecting the car and making the payment through your preferred method. You can choose to pay online or opt for financing. 

  5. Enjoy your Car

    Once the purchase is complete, you can drive your pre-owned car backed by our support. 

 

Additional Services at Cars24

Trade-in Option

You can easily trade in your current car to reduce the cost of your second hand car purchase. We also offer to buy your old car, and we’ll apply its value as a reduction towards your next used car from us. 

Car Valuation

Utilise our free online car valuation tool to determine the market value of your vehicle. To use our free calculator, simply enter your car’s details, schedule a free video inspection and receive a valuation.

Roadworthy Certificate

Use our Roadworthy Certificate services to ensure that your vehicle meets safety standards, starting at $199. We offer same day inspections and repair services with free re-inspection within 14 days.

Car History Check

Know more about your next car with the Check Vehicle History by Cars24. This comprehensive car history report verifies your vehicle’s background and accident report. 

Extended Warranty

Protect your used car with our extended warranty options. In addition to the three-month standard warranty coverage, you can choose Platinum Coverage and get your car’s warranty extended. 

Finance Pre-Approved

Secure financing with ease through our online pre-approved loans process. Obtain a decision in just 2 minutes without impacting your credit score and explore competitive interest rates tailored to your needs. 

Frequently Asked Questions

  • What is the starting range of a used car in Australia at Cars24?

     The starting range of a used car in Australia is $7990.

  • Can I test drive before buying a used car in Australia?

    Yes, test drives are available for Cars24 certified, but the process varies from dealer to dealer. You can arrange it directly once you contact the dealer.

  • What if the car doesn’t meet expectations after delivery?

    Cars24 certified cars offer a 7-day return policy, where you can return the car if you aren’t satisfied with it.

  • Are Prices negotiable or fixed?

    Our pricing is clear and transparent; therefore, there is no room for negotiation. However, if you opt to trade in, you can get a deduction of the same value as your current car. 

  • Can I see the car’s history report before buying a used car in Australia?

    Yes, Cars24 offers you to review the PPSR report before making the final purchase of a used car.
